Cactus Code Thorn SphericalInfall
Thorn Author(s)     : Roland Haas <roland.haas@physics.gatech.edu>
                      Tanja Bode <tanja.bode@physics.gatech.edu>
Thorn Maintainer(s) : Tanja Bode <tanja.bode@physics.gatech.edu>
--------------------------------------------------------------------------

Purpose of the thorn:

Provides simple initial data for radial infalling test dust into a
Schwarzschild black hole by following ApJ 277:296 (Hawley et al).

Expanded to initialize real Bondi solution as found by evolving 
outwards from the sonic point on an isotropic spacetime.
